2. The 15th day of November 2022 is appointed as the day on which the 
Bretton Woods Agreements (Amendment) Act 2022 (No. 36 of 2022) shall 
come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

11 November, 2022. 

PASCHAL DONOHOE, 
Minister for Finance. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 15th November, 2022.
